Description:
    The task_handler generator creates a new Tasker task handler with the
    necessary configuration files, step handlers, and specs. It sets up the
    structure for implementing a Tasker workflow based on a YAML configuration.

Example:
    rails generate task_handler OrderProcess

    This will create:
        config/tasks/order_process.yaml
        app/tasks/order_process.rb
        app/tasks/order_process/step_handler.rb
        spec/tasks/order_process_spec.rb

Options:
    --module-namespace=NAMESPACE   # The module namespace for the task handler
                                   # Default: Task

    --concurrent=true|false        # Whether the task can be run concurrently
                                   # Default: true

    --dependent-system=SYSTEM      # The default dependent system for the task
                                   # Default: default_system
